{"lemma":"أَخْيَلٌ","slug":"أَخْيَلٌ","root":"خ.#.ل","root_slug":"خ-_-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-_-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11887"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AE%D9%92%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11887","headword_ar":"اَخْيَلُ","root":"xyl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most, proud and self-conceited."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axowalu","text_ar":"اَخْوَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xwl","text_ar":"خول"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Occurring in several provs.; as, for ex.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoyalu mino guraAbK","text_ar":"اَخْيَلُ مِنْ غُرَابٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More proud and self-conceited than a crow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"grAb","text_ar":"غراب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is proud and self-conceited in its gait. (Meyd.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayalaA='u","text_ar":"خَيَلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAl","text_ar":"خَال"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning [a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing resembling"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pimple, inclining to blackness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon his face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxiylN","text_ar":"مَخِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyuwlN","text_ar":"مَخْيُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxuwlN","text_ar":"مَخُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maquwlN","text_ar":"مَقُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) this last belonging to art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xwl","text_ar":"خول"},{"kind":"text","text":", as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlN","text_ar":"خَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", whence it is derived, does in one dial., (Msb,) A man (S, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marked with"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiylaAn","text_ar":"خِيلَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moles"},{"kind":"text","text":"upon his person]: (S, Msb, K: *) fem. [of the first]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayolaA='u","text_ar":"خَيْلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^axayolu","text_ar":"الاَخَيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) when indeterminate, ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axayolN","text_ar":"اَخَيْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axayolu","text_ar":"اَخَيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] perfectly decl., [thus] used as a subst., but some make it imperfectly decl. both when determinate and when indeterminate, and assert it to be originally an epithet, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~axay~ulu","text_ar":"التَّخَيُّلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) [though accord. to others it seems to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoyalu","text_ar":"اَخْيَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning “ having many moles, ”]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain bird,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded as of evil omen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that alights upon the rump of the camel, and is app. for that reason held to be of evil omen;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA; [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyuwlN","text_ar":"مَخْيُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) [applied in the present day to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the green wood-pecker, picus viridis;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Surad","text_ar":"صُرَد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the green"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Surad","text_ar":"صُرَد"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iqir~aAq","text_ar":"شِقِرَّاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a name likewise now applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the green wood-pecker,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the common roller, coracias garrula"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Fr, S, Msb, K:) so called because upon its wings are colours differing from its general colour: (Skr, TA:) or so called because diversified with black and white: (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAhiyn","text_ar":"شَاهِين"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species of falcon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (JK, TA, and Ham p. 705:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axaAyilu","text_ar":"اَخَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, T, S, Msb, TA, and Ham ubi suprà,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiylN","text_ar":"خِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","S","Msb","K","O","JK","TA","Fr","Skr"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%A3%D8%AE%D9%8A%D9%84/","headword_ar":"أخيلة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_32","lexicon_en":"Supplément aux dictionnaires arabes by Reinhart Dozy (d. 1883 CE)","lexicon_ar":"تكملة المعاجم العربية لرينهارت دوزي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=49500#256096","body_html":"أخيلة: جمعها أخايل: دبوس (ألكالا) وهي تصحيف كلمة أخلة جمع خلال التي تدل على نفس المعنى."}]}}